Display clear.
KernelInstaller fileInClassChunks: 'RecorzKernelClass: #KeywordExpressionReporter superclass: #Object instanceVariableNames: ''''
!
show: text
    ^Transcript show: text
!'.
KernelInstaller rememberObject: ((KernelInstaller classNamed: 'KeywordExpressionReporter') new) named: 'keywordExpressionReporter'.
Transcript show: 'EXPR'.
Transcript cr.
((KernelInstaller objectNamed: 'keywordExpressionReporter') show: 'RETURN').
